titles.title: A bill to suspend temporarily the duty on 2,5-Dichloro-e,6-Bis(9-Ethyl-3-Carbazolylamino)-1,4-Benzoquinone(Dianil).

action.text: Read twice and referred to the Committee on Finance.

bill.summary: 10/29/2009--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to suspend temporarily the duty on 2,5-Dichloro-e,6-Bis(9-Ethyl-3-Carbazolylamino)-1,4-Benzoquinone(Dianil).
